# ============================================
# Quick Start:
# ============================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your actual values above
# 3. Generate strong JWT_SECRET (see instructions above)
# 4. Configure email provider (Gmail recommended for development)
# 5. Start MongoDB: mongod
# 6. Run: npm run dev
